enum.name: TCIO
enum.abstract: Specification on variable to define its quality.

class.name: CATIBKTBehaviorSettingAtt
class.abstract: Enables attribute access to BKT options.

method.name: GetBKTAccessRights
method.abstract: Retrieves the BKTAccessRights attribute.

method.name: GetBKTAccessRightsInfo
method.abstract: Retrieves the state of the BKTAccessRights parameter.

method.name: GetBKTBehaviorOperationMessage
method.abstract: Retrieves or sets the BKTBehaviorOperationMessage parameter.

method.name: GetBKTBehaviorOperationMessageInfo
method.abstract: Retrieves the state of the BKTBehaviorOperationMessage parameter.

method.name: GetBKTSpecificationTree
method.abstract: Retrieves the BKTSpecificationTree parameter.

method.name: GetBKTSpecificationTreeInfo
method.abstract: Retrieves the state of the BKTSpecificationTree parameter.

method.name: SetBKTAccessRights
method.abstract: Sets the BKTAccessRights attribute.

method.name: SetBKTAccessRightsLock
method.abstract: Locks or unlocks the BKTAccessRights parameter.

method.name: SetBKTBehaviorOperationMessage
method.abstract: Sets the BKTBehaviorOperationMessage parameter.

method.name: SetBKTBehaviorOperationMessageLock
method.abstract: Locks or unlocks the BKTBehaviorOperationMessage parameter.

method.name: SetBKTSpecificationTree
method.abstract: Sets the BKTSpecificationTree parameter.

method.name: SetBKTSpecificationTreeLock
method.abstract: Locks or unlocks the BKTSpecificationTree parameter.

class.name: CATIVariableManagement
class.abstract: Interface to manage the variables of behaviors and Dynamic Types (Tecnological Objects).

method.name: GetLinkedVariable
method.abstract: Retrieves the variable or the feature pointed via the link.

method.name: GetUserAccess
method.abstract: Retreives the user acces mode of a variable of a given quality.

method.name: GetVariable
method.abstract: Retreives a variable of a given quality.

method.name: GetVariableAccess
method.abstract: Retreives the name and quality of a variable.

method.name: GetVariableInfos
method.abstract: Retreives the characteristics of a variable of a given quality.

method.name: GetVariableType
method.abstract: Retreives the Knowledgeware type of the object pointed by a variable of a given quality.

method.name: GetVariableValue
method.abstract: Retreives the value of a variable of a given quality.

method.name: GetVariablesNames
method.abstract: Returns the variables names matching given criterion.

method.name: IsLocalVariable
method.abstract: Indicates if a variable of a given quality is local to this object.

method.name: LinkVariables
method.abstract: Creates a link between two variables.

method.name: SetVariableType
method.abstract: Sets the expected knowledgeware type of the object pointed by a variable of a given quality.

method.name: SetVariableValue
method.abstract: Valuates a variable of a given quality.

method.name: Unset
method.abstract: Unsets a variable.
